00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,070
confidently committing perjury.

291
00:13:02,070 --> 00:13:03,110
Your Honor.

292
00:13:03,790 --> 00:13:05,990
The opposing attorney is not questioning the witness.

293
00:13:05,990 --> 00:13:07,650
He's expressing his opinion.

294
00:13:07,780 --> 00:13:10,580
