295
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:14,640
Yes.

296
00:13:18,330 --> 00:13:18,970
Witness.

297
00:13:20,180 --> 00:13:21,780
Did you come to testify today

298
00:13:23,070 --> 00:13:25,110
because you ran out of money for drugs?

299
00:13:25,110 --> 00:13:27,430
-That's why you want to get some from Yang...
-Your Honor.

300
00:13:27,430 --> 00:13:29,590
The opposing attorney is attacking the witness.

301
00:13:29,590 --> 00:13:30,190
No.

302
00:13:30,190 --> 00:13:32,070
Yang Weida raped me.

303
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:33,780
I was raped.

304
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:36,710
Yang Weida

305
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:38,350
is a beast.

306
00:14:04,860 --> 00:14:05,860
What a real drama.

307
00:14:08,130 --> 00:14:14,480
[Jingbei Court]

308
00:14:09,820 --> 00:14:10,980
The court believes

309
00:14:11,470 --> 00:14:13,070
there isn't enough evidence

310
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:16,680
to prove the alleged sexual harassment by the plaintiff.

311
00:14:17,110 --> 00:14:17,870
Therefore,

312
00:14:18,110 --> 00:14:19,320
the court rules to

313
00:14:20,110 --> 00:14:21,420
dismiss the plaintiff's lawsuit

314
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:23,700
in accordance with the law.

315
00:14:24,060 --> 00:14:27,920
The plaintiff is responsible for the case acceptance fee of 500 yuan.

316
00:14:29,610 --> 00:14:30,940
The court is adjourned.

317
00:14:50,780 --> 00:14:51,380
Guo Yu.

318
00:15:04,110 --> 00:15:05,350
Explain it to us.

319
00:15:05,380 --> 00:15:06,550
Explain it.

320
00:15:29,230 --> 00:15:30,430
Are you still a human?

321
00:15:33,250 --> 00:15:34,420
Why not?

322
00:15:34,940 --> 00:15:36,470
Am I not Unscrupulous Chen?

323
00:15:38,810 --> 00:15:39,340
What?

324
00:15:39,640 --> 00:15:41,230
You came all the way here in the middle of the night

325
00:15:41,230 --> 00:15:42,230
to scold me?

326
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,790
You deserve much worse than me scolding you.

327
00:15:43,790 --> 00:15:44,710
How could you take Yang Weida's money

328
00:15:44,710 --> 00:15:46,230
without a clear conscience?

329
00:15:46,230 --> 00:15:48,240
Why can't I take Yang Weida's money

330
00:15:48,270 --> 00:15:50,020
with a clear conscience?

331
00:15:52,260 --> 00:15:53,270
I did my job.

332
00:15:53,300 --> 00:15:54,220
I won the lawsuit

333
00:15:54,220 --> 00:15:55,480
because of my ability.

334
00:15:55,630 --> 00:15:57,370
Why did you come here to challenge me?

335
00:15:57,370 --> 00:15:59,770
You're Yang Weida's lawyer. That's right.

336
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:01,140
It's your duty

337
00:16:01,170 --> 00:16:02,410
to defend him.

338
00:16:02,590 --> 00:16:03,830
But how could you

339
00:16:03,830 --> 00:16:05,310
play such dirty tricks in court?

340
00:16:05,310 --> 00:16:06,830
Your tactics against Xia Linlin were heartless.

341
00:16:06,830 --> 00:16:08,190
Do you have any humanity left?

342
00:16:08,190 --> 00:16:11,450
If I had humanity, I wouldn't be called Unscrupulous Chen.

343
00:16:13,630 --> 00:16:14,480
Ms. Luo,

344
00:16:14,930 --> 00:16:15,710
do you still not know

345
00:16:15,710 --> 00:16:17,470
how you lost the lawsuit?

346
00:16:18,310 --> 00:16:19,110
I admit

347
00:16:20,030 --> 00:16:22,240
Xia Linlin hid the content of the messages from us.

348
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:24,580
It was our negligence at work.

349
00:16:24,820 --> 00:16:26,400
But given how Yang Weida

350
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:27,500
harmed Xia Linlin,

351
00:16:27,610 --> 00:16:29,600
you still forced her to embarrass herself in court.

352
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,870
Do you realize the additional damage

353
00:16:30,870 --> 00:16:32,660
you caused to her?

354
00:16:32,830 --> 00:16:33,830
Do you even have a conscience?

355
00:16:33,830 --> 00:16:35,170
You're wrong.

356
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:43,880
Xia Linlin

357
00:16:44,870 --> 00:16:46,130
was the witness you brought.

358
00:16:46,130 --> 00:16:47,760
She's not the plaintiff.

359
00:16:47,890 --> 00:16:49,680
Your client's name is Guo Yu.

360
00:16:49,710 --> 00:16:50,990
You should prioritize

361
00:16:51,010 --> 00:16:52,250
Guo Yu's interests.

362
00:16:53,590 --> 00:16:55,490
Xia Linlin is pitiful, I admit,

363
00:16:55,630 --> 00:16:56,430
so what?

364
00:16:56,830 --> 00:16:57,960
You're a lawyer.

365
00:16:58,230 --> 00:16:59,870
A lawyer

366
00:16:59,870 --> 00:17:01,280
shouldn't let their sympathy

367
00:17:01,280 --> 00:17:03,100
influence their judgment.

368
00:17:04,810 --> 00:17:05,640
Xia Linlin

369
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:06,869
concealed

370
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,540
all the unfavorable message content.

371
00:17:08,540 --> 00:17:10,160
It's understandable from a human perspective,

372
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:11,220
but what about you?

373
00:17:11,430 --> 00:17:13,270
You're Guo Yu's lawyer.

374
00:17:13,670 --> 00:17:15,000
Because you sympathized with Xia Linlin,

375
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:16,710
you ignored all potential risks

376
00:17:16,710 --> 00:17:18,560
and failed to protect your client's interests.

377
00:17:18,560 --> 00:17:20,040
It was your fault.

378
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:22,510
Also,

379
00:17:23,510 --> 00:17:25,310
why are you here arguing with me?

380
00:17:25,380 --> 00:17:26,780
What are you arguing for?

381
00:17:27,069 --> 00:17:28,270
If you have time to argue,

382
00:17:28,270 --> 00:17:29,410
why don't you persuade Guo Yu

383
00:17:29,410 --> 00:17:30,610
to appeal?

384
00:17:30,990 --> 00:17:33,070
If you think Yang Weida is guilty,

385
00:17:33,090 --> 00:17:35,110
put your energy

386
00:17:35,140 --> 00:17:36,550
into finding evidence to nail him,

387
00:17:36,550 --> 00:17:37,510
instead of coming here

388
00:17:37,510 --> 00:17:39,230
to seek for justice.

389
00:17:41,790 --> 00:17:42,310
Also,

390
00:17:45,130 --> 00:17:46,270
don't you call me Unscrupulous Chen?

391
00:17:46,270 --> 00:17:47,470
Well, maybe I am unscrupulous.

392
00:17:47,470 --> 00:17:49,800
I still have plenty of tricks up my sleeve.

393
00:17:49,950 --> 00:17:51,210
You want justice, huh?

394
00:17:51,220 --> 00:17:53,190
Put aside those

395
00:17:53,190 --> 00:17:53,950
amateur overflowing sympathies.

396
00:17:53,950 --> 00:17:55,510
Win against me first.

397
00:18:24,790 --> 00:18:26,900
If you think Yang Weida is guilty,

398
00:18:26,930 --> 00:18:28,960
put your energy

399
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:30,310
into finding evidence to nail him,

400
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:31,420
instead of coming here

401
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:33,070
to seek for justice.

402
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:15,660
Chen Shuo was right.

403
00:19:16,310 --> 00:19:18,430
We indeed lost our judgment

404
00:19:18,470 --> 00:19:19,710
because of Xia Linlin's evidence

405
00:19:19,710 --> 00:19:22,310
and failed to make the best decision for Guo Yu.

406
00:19:26,140 --> 00:19:26,750
I...

407
00:19:27,390 --> 00:19:28,270
I even went

408
00:19:28,290 --> 00:19:30,230
to give Unscrupulous Chen a piece of my mind.

409
00:19:30,230 --> 00:19:30,830
Look at me.

410
00:19:31,330 --> 00:19:33,620
What a solid comeback from him.

411
00:19:34,230 --> 00:19:36,150
He left me speechless.

412
00:19:36,150 --> 00:19:37,680
I wished I could find a hole

413
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:38,910
to crawl into.

414
00:19:39,140 --> 00:19:41,670
I was acting I couldn't handle defeat, right?

415
00:19:43,270 --> 00:19:45,670
Yeah, you're quite bad at handling defeat.

416
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:48,470
If I weren't Guo Yu's lawyer

417
00:19:48,790 --> 00:19:50,920
and sitting in the spectator's seat,

418
00:19:52,100 --> 00:19:53,830
I would've applauded Chen Shuo

419
00:19:54,350 --> 00:19:55,880
for this splendid victory.

420
00:19:56,330 --> 00:19:58,260
Let's toast to Unscrupulous Chen.

421
00:20:05,550 --> 00:20:07,680
I wonder how Guo Yu is feeling tonight.

422
00:20:10,990 --> 00:20:13,120
She must be going through a rough time.

423
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:19,980
I hope she can be stronger than us.

424
00:20:23,060 --> 00:20:24,890
Why must she be strong?

425
00:20:25,470 --> 00:20:26,550
It was our fault,

426
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:28,830
not hers.

427
00:20:31,370 --> 00:20:32,990
Do you think she will appeal?

428
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:34,990
Probably not.

429
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:38,940
The case has already ended up like this. There's no need to.

430
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:45,880
It's just hard to accept.

431
00:21:02,430 --> 00:21:03,290
Here she comes.

432
00:21:03,790 --> 00:21:04,630
Guo Yu.

433
00:21:04,830 --> 00:21:05,470
Guo Yu.

434
00:21:05,470 --> 00:21:07,710
What do you want to say about this verdict?

435
00:21:07,710 --> 00:21:08,570
Say something.

436
00:21:08,790 --> 00:21:09,310
Guo Yu.

437
00:21:11,990 --> 00:21:13,470
Say something.

438
00:21:13,470 --> 00:21:14,840
We've been waiting for you.

439
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:16,460
What do you want to say? Say something.

440
00:21:16,460 --> 00:21:16,950
Stop filming.

441
00:21:16,950 --> 00:21:18,720
Excuse me. Stop filming.

442
00:21:18,760 --> 00:21:19,990
Guo Yu! Guo Yu!

443
00:21:20,060 --> 00:21:21,300
Guo Yu! Guo Yu!

444
00:21:21,800 --> 00:21:22,920
Guo Yu.

445
00:21:23,350 --> 00:21:24,230
I'm a lawyer.

446
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:24,910
My client

447
00:21:24,910 --> 00:21:26,230
has no obligation to accept your interview.

448
00:21:26,230 --> 00:21:27,690
Stop harassing her, okay?

449
00:21:27,810 --> 00:21:29,800
Guo Yu, say something.

450
00:21:29,820 --> 00:21:31,320
Guo Yu, say something.

451
00:21:36,260 --> 00:21:37,400
Ms. Luo. Ms. Qiu.

452
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:39,800
Take a seat anywhere.

453
00:21:43,870 --> 00:21:44,550
Guo Yu.

454
00:21:44,950 --> 00:21:46,230
Are you

455
00:21:47,150 --> 00:21:49,810
planning to pack up and return to your hometown?

456
00:21:50,790 --> 00:21:51,470
Are you…

457
00:21:52,310 --> 00:21:53,640
Are you going to give up?

458
00:21:54,480 --> 00:21:55,270
I lost.

459
00:21:57,220 --> 00:21:57,710
Guo Yu.

460
00:21:57,710 --> 00:22:00,110
Actually, we still have a chance to appeal.

461
00:22:00,470 --> 00:22:01,540
Ms. Luo, Ms. Qiu,

462
00:22:03,150 --> 00:22:05,310
thank you for everything you've done for me.

463
00:22:05,310 --> 00:22:06,910
I told you from the beginning

464
00:22:06,970 --> 00:22:09,430
that I was prepared for this to be a lost case.

465
00:22:10,030 --> 00:22:12,360
I just wanted to give myself some closure.

466
00:22:13,520 --> 00:22:14,750
Now, I have it,

467
00:22:15,130 --> 00:22:15,920
even...

468
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:17,770
more than expected.

469
00:22:19,790 --> 00:22:20,790
I understand now.

470
00:22:20,830 --> 00:22:22,460
An egg can't beat a stone.

471
00:22:23,100 --> 00:22:24,670
Arms can't twist a thigh.

472
00:22:26,550 --> 00:22:29,280
Thank you for choosing to stand by the egg's side.

473
00:22:29,700 --> 00:22:31,300
But, even with your support,

474
00:22:31,950 --> 00:22:33,210
it's still not enough.

475
00:22:36,030 --> 00:22:36,750
So,

476
00:22:37,990 --> 00:22:39,100
it's all over.

477
00:22:39,630 --> 00:22:41,290
I'm going back to my hometown.

478
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:45,310
Guo Yu.

479
00:22:45,560 --> 00:22:46,960
Lawsuits may end,

480
00:22:46,990 --> 00:22:49,520
but you don't have to go back to your hometown.

481
00:22:50,670 --> 00:22:52,750
How can I stay in Jingbei

482
00:22:53,550 --> 00:22:54,910
after this case?

483
00:22:55,120 --> 00:22:56,480
You don't have to stay in Jingbei.

484
00:22:56,480 --> 00:22:57,560
You can go somewhere else,

485
00:22:57,560 --> 00:22:59,490
but don't go back to your hometown.

486
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:00,630
Once you go back,

487
00:23:01,340 --> 00:23:03,540
it means you choose your original life.

488
00:23:04,240 --> 00:23:07,040
Can you really adapt to the original environment?

489
00:23:08,990 --> 00:23:10,190
Let me think about it.

490
00:23:11,990 --> 00:23:13,200
Ms. Luo, Ms. Qiu,

491
00:23:14,230 --> 00:23:14,990
thank you.

492
00:23:15,970 --> 00:23:18,100
Guo Yu, take some time to think it over.

493
00:23:18,190 --> 00:23:19,590
If you have any thoughts,

494
00:23:19,760 --> 00:23:21,290
you can contact us anytime.

495
00:23:36,650 --> 00:23:38,570
This is the price of idealism.

496
00:23:40,230 --> 00:23:40,910
Qiu Hua.

497
00:23:41,950 --> 00:23:42,990
It was my fault.

498
00:23:43,650 --> 00:23:45,090
You've always been more practical than me.

499
00:23:45,090 --> 00:23:46,250
I dragged you down.

500
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:53,020
But it doesn't matter.

501
00:23:53,090 --> 00:23:55,370
"If a man in the morning learn the truth, he may die in the evening without regret."

502
00:23:55,370 --> 00:23:57,060
Besides, we're just first-year lawyers.

503
00:23:57,060 --> 00:23:58,990
It's never too late to understand.

504
00:24:01,190 --> 00:24:02,480
From now on,

505
00:24:04,140 --> 00:24:05,940
I'll never take cases like this.

506
00:24:07,080 --> 00:24:08,670
Idealism

507
00:24:08,690 --> 00:24:09,760
and the grand concept of justice?

508
00:24:09,760 --> 00:24:12,500
I won't touch them even if you smash them on my head.

509
00:24:12,500 --> 00:24:13,800
If I make the same mistake again,

510
00:24:13,800 --> 00:24:14,710
just kick me.

511
00:24:16,990 --> 00:24:19,030
When we get back,

512
00:24:19,120 --> 00:24:21,700
let's find Mr. Tao and get back that patent case.

513
00:24:21,700 --> 00:24:23,150
We're already in the league of lawyers

514
00:24:23,150 --> 00:24:25,750
earning a few hundred thousand a year.

515
00:24:26,670 --> 00:24:28,130
As long as we don't mess up,

516
00:24:28,230 --> 00:24:29,270
making a few million a year

517
00:24:29,270 --> 00:24:30,750
is just a matter of time.

518
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:33,130
Aim higher,

519
00:24:34,230 --> 00:24:35,750
in ten years or so,

520
00:24:35,800 --> 00:24:38,530
surpassing Fang Lihong might not be impossible.

521
00:24:41,760 --> 00:24:42,820
Come to think of it,

522
00:24:43,620 --> 00:24:44,950
it's quite optimistic.

523
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:47,710
By the way,

524
00:24:48,280 --> 00:24:50,960
who was the fan

525
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:53,170
that gave you flowers at the courthouse yesterday?

526
00:24:53,170 --> 00:24:54,320
Your boyfriend?

527
00:24:54,570 --> 00:24:56,360
Not now.

528
00:24:57,070 --> 00:24:58,470
Maybe in the future.

529
00:24:58,990 --> 00:25:00,040
How is he?

530
00:25:00,950 --> 00:25:02,220
He's okay.

531
00:25:03,300 --> 00:25:05,210
He's nice to me.

532
00:25:07,310 --> 00:25:08,150
He's loyal.

533
00:25:09,150 --> 00:25:10,230
Come on, Qiu Hua.

534
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:12,620
Being loyal is enough for you?

535
00:25:15,430 --> 00:25:18,990
I might not have been satisfied before,

536
00:25:18,990 --> 00:25:20,590
but now that I think about it,

537
00:25:20,990 --> 00:25:22,270
it might not be bad.

538
00:25:22,990 --> 00:25:23,950
Why?

539
00:25:23,990 --> 00:25:24,870
Security.

540
00:25:26,230 --> 00:25:27,990
Well, as long as you want,

541
00:25:28,100 --> 00:25:29,710
you can earn hundreds of thousands a year.

542
00:25:29,710 --> 00:25:31,350
How can you not feel secure?

543
00:25:31,790 --> 00:25:32,550
Come on.

544
00:25:32,870 --> 00:25:33,950
Look at me,

545
00:25:34,660 --> 00:25:36,590
carrying over ten million in debt.

546
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:38,430
I'm different from you.

547
00:25:38,750 --> 00:25:40,280
His name is Zhang Quanquan.

548
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:43,630
This name sounds quite secure.

549
00:25:44,710 --> 00:25:46,080
It sounds complete.

550
00:25:49,890 --> 00:25:52,290
Don't blame me for being straightforward.

551
00:25:55,070 --> 00:25:57,470
I just think you deserve better.

552
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:01,420
After going through so many things,

553
00:26:01,630 --> 00:26:03,470
if you could choose again,

554
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:05,930
wouldn't you consider security?

555
00:26:06,780 --> 00:26:07,640
I'm being nosy.

556
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:08,170
My bad.

557
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:09,320
I won't ask again.

558
00:26:13,390 --> 00:26:14,780
I know you care about me.

559
00:26:18,570 --> 00:26:20,560
You'll get through this bridge in a while,

560
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:22,630
then drop me off at the subway station.

561
00:26:22,630 --> 00:26:23,430
Where are you going?

562
00:26:23,430 --> 00:26:24,690
I have something to do.

563
00:26:28,230 --> 00:26:28,990
Fine.

564
00:26:36,370 --> 00:26:38,850
I didn't agree to take this case from the beginning.

565
00:26:38,850 --> 00:26:40,090
Now what's the result?

566
00:26:40,090 --> 00:26:41,760
We ended up with a drug addict

567
00:26:41,790 --> 00:26:43,050
testifying in court,

568
00:26:43,390 --> 00:26:45,670
making our law firm a laughingstock.

569
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:46,950
What a bad influence it made

570
00:26:46,950 --> 00:26:48,610
to our company's reputation.

571
00:26:55,080 --> 00:26:56,830
Han, it's just a losing case.

572
00:26:57,120 --> 00:26:58,240
It is a case,

573
00:26:58,930 --> 00:27:00,940
but is it just a case?

574
00:27:01,510 --> 00:27:03,430
We can lose a case,

575
00:27:03,550 --> 00:27:05,550
